com.datumbox.common.persistentstorage.mapdb

Class MapDBConnector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datumbox.common.persistentstorage.AutoCloseConnector
      • com.datumbox.common.persistentstorage.mapdb.MapDBConnector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DatabaseConnector, AutoCloseable

    public class MapDBConnector
extends AutoCloseConnector
    The MapDBConnector is responsible for saving and loading data from MapDB files, creating BigMaps which are backed by files and persisting data. The MapDBConnector does not load all the contents of BigMaps in memory, maintains an LRU cache to speed up data retrieval and persists all data in MapDB files.
    Author:
    Vasilis Vryniotis
